<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0c1022">
<title>WK 2026 — Moby's Prediction Model</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:wdth,wght@62..125,400..900&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg:#0c1022;--bg2:#121736;--panel:#171d3f;--panel2:#1d2450;--line:#2a3162;--text:#e8eaf6;--muted:#8b93c4;--gold:#f5c84c;--elo:#4c9af5;--form:#f5774c;--xg:#4cf5a8;--squad:#b54cf5;--warn:#f5564c;--third:#f5a623}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5}
.wrap{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px 80px}
header{padding:42px 0 26px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.eyebrow{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.22em;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase}
h1{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-stretch:115%;font-weight:850;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);line-height:1.02;margin:10px 0 8px;text-transform:uppercase}
h1 span{color:var(--gold)}
.sub{color:var(--muted);max-width:680px}
.sub b{color:var(--text)}
nav{display:flex;gap:4px;margin:26px 0 30px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);flex-wrap:wrap}
nav button{background:none;border:none;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;padding:12px 18px;cursor:pointer;border-bottom:3px solid transparent}
nav button:hover{color:var(--text)}
nav button.active{color:var(--gold);border-bottom-color:var(--gold)}
nav button:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:-2px}
.page{display:none}
.page.active{display:block;animation:fade .25s ease}
@keyframes fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
h2{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:20px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:6px}
.note{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:22px}
.legend{display:flex;gap:18px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:18px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.legend span{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:2px;display:inline-block}
.flag{font-size:16px;margin-right:6px}
.rank-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:34px 178px 1fr 64px;gap:12px;align-items:center;padding:7px 10px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .12s}
.rank-row:hover{background:var(--panel)}
.rank-num{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;text-align:right}
.rank-team{font-weight:600;font-size:13.5px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.rank-team .pool-tag{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:6px}
.bar-track{height:20px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;display:flex}
.bar-seg{height:100%}
.rank-val{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);text-align:right}
.excl{font-size:9px;color:var(--warn);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;margin-left:5px}
.detail{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(8,10,24,.78);display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:50;padding:20px}
.detail.open{display:flex}
.detail-card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;max-width:640px;width:100%;padding:28px;max-height:88vh;overflow-y:auto}
.detail-card h3{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:24px;text-transform:uppercase}
.detail-card .close{float:right;background:none;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);border-radius:6px;padding:4px 10px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px}
.stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-top:18px}
.stat{background:var(--bg2);border-radius:8px;padding:12px}
.stat .lbl{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}
.stat .val{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:17px;margin-top:3px}
.hist-title{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin:22px 0 10px}
.hist-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px}
.hist-table th{text-align:left;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--muted);padding:5px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.hist-table td{padding:6px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg2)}
.hist-table td.mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
.wdl-W{color:var(--xg);font-weight:600}.wdl-D{color:var(--gold);font-weight:600}.wdl-L{color:var(--warn);font-weight:600}
.pool-select{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:18px}
.pool-select button{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--panel);color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer}
.pool-select button:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--text)}
.pool-select button.active{background:var(--gold);color:#1a1505;border-color:var(--gold)}
.subtabs{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:20px}
.subtabs button{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer}
.subtabs button.active{background:var(--pan2,var(--panel2));color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold)}
.pool-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(290px,1fr));gap:16px}
.team-card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:18px;cursor:pointer}
.team-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold)}
.team-card h4{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:16px;text-transform:uppercase;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;gap:8px}
.team-card h4 .cs{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:15px;color:var(--gold)}
.team-card .meta{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin:4px 0 12px}
.mini-rows{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}
.mini-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:52px 1fr 44px;gap:8px;align-items:center;font-size:11px}
.mini-row .l{color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase}
.mini-track{height:8px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}
.mini-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px}
.mini-row .v{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;text-align:right}
.pool-matches{margin-top:26px}
.pool-matches h3{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.standings{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13.5px;background:var(--panel);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.standings th{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--muted);text-align:left;padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--panel2)}
.standings td{padding:11px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg2)}
.standings td.mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
.standings tr.qual td{background:rgba(76,245,168,.05)}
.standings tr.qual td:first-child{border-left:3px solid var(--xg)}
.standings tr.third td{background:rgba(245,166,35,.07)}
.standings tr.third td:first-child{border-left:3px solid var(--third)}
.qual-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px}
.sort-bar{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:14px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.sort-bar span{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}
.sort-bar button{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer}
.sort-bar button.active{color:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold)}
.slider-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.slider-bar label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}
.slider-bar input[type=range]{width:220px;accent-color:var(--gold)}
.slider-bar .slider-val{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);min-width:46px}
.slider-bar .count{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:auto}
.match{display:grid;grid-template-columns:74px 1fr 130px 90px;gap:14px;align-items:center;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:8px}
.match.clickable{cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .12s}
.match.clickable:hover{border-color:var(--gold)}
.match .when{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted)}
.match .teams{font-weight:600;font-size:13.5px}
.match .teams .vs{color:var(--muted);font-weight:400;margin:0 7px;font-size:11px}
.match .pool-badge{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--gold);background:var(--bg2);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;margin-left:8px}
.match .pred{font-size:12px}
.match .pred .who{font-weight:600;color:var(--gold)}
.match .pred.tctc .who{color:var(--muted);font-style:italic}
.conf-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.conf-track{flex:1;height:7px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}
.conf-fill{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--warn),var(--gold) 60%,var(--xg))}
.conf-val{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);min-width:32px;text-align:right}
.scatter-box{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;margin-bottom:24px;position:relative}
svg text{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
.tooltip{position:absolute;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--gold);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:12.5px;pointer-events:none;display:none;z-index:10;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.tooltip .tt-name{font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px}
.tooltip .tt-row{color:var(--muted)}
.tooltip .tt-row b{color:var(--text);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-weight:500}
.scatter-pt{cursor:pointer}
.scatter-pt:hover{stroke:#fff;stroke-width:2}
.disagree-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px}
.disagree-table th{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--muted);text-align:left;padding:8px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.disagree-table td{padding:9px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg2)}
.disagree-table td.mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
.gap-pos{color:var(--xg)}.gap-neg{color:var(--warn)}
.match-detail-meta{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;margin:4px 0 16px}
.md-compare{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12.5px;margin-top:6px}
.md-compare th{text-align:left;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);padding:6px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.md-compare td{padding:7px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg2)}
.md-compare td.mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
.md-pred{background:var(--bg2);border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin:16px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.map-frame{width:100%;height:280px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;margin-top:16px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#0a0d1c}
.map-tile{position:absolute;width:256px;height:256px;user-select:none;pointer-events:none}
.map-pin{position:absolute;left:50%;top:50%;width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);border:3px solid #1a1505;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(245,200,76,.35),0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.6);transform:translate(-50%,-50%);z-index:5}
.map-note a{color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none}
.map-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px}
.live-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:18px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.live-bar button{background:var(--gold);color:#1a1505;border:none;font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.05em;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:7px;cursor:pointer}
.live-bar button:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:wait}
.live-status{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(160px,1fr));gap:12px;margin-bottom:24px}
.card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:16px}
.card .lbl{font-size:10.5px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em}
.card .big{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:850;font-size:28px;margin-top:4px}
.card .small{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
.live-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:64px 1fr 120px 96px 110px;gap:12px;align-items:center;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:7px}
.live-row .when{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}
.live-row .teams{font-weight:600;font-size:13px}
.live-row .teams .vs{color:var(--muted);font-weight:400;margin:0 6px;font-size:10px}
.live-row .pred-small{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}
.live-row .pred-small b{color:var(--gold);font-weight:600}
.score-in{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;justify-content:center}
.score-in input{width:38px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--text);border-radius:5px;padding:5px 4px;text-align:center;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:13px}
.score-in input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--gold)}
.score-in .dash{color:var(--muted)}
.outcome{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;text-align:center;padding:5px 8px;border-radius:5px}
.outcome.ok{background:rgba(76,245,168,.12);color:var(--xg)}
.outcome.bad{background:rgba(245,86,76,.12);color:var(--warn)}
.outcome.half{background:rgba(245,200,76,.12);color:var(--gold)}
.outcome.tctc{background:var(--bg2);color:var(--muted)}
.outcome.pending{color:var(--muted);background:none;border:1px dashed var(--line)}
.calib{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:12px;margin:18px 0 26px}
.live-src{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:18px}
.live-pool-h{font-family:'Archivo',sans-serif;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold);margin:22px 0 10px}
.method-block p,.method-block li{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px}
@media(max-width:720px){
  .wrap{padding:0 14px 70px}
  header{padding:30px 0 20px}
  nav{gap:0;margin:20px 0 24px;overflow-x:auto;flex-wrap:nowrap;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch}
  nav button{padding:11px 13px;font-size:12px;white-space:nowrap;flex:0 0 auto}
  .rank-row{grid-template-columns:24px 1fr 56px;gap:8px;row-gap:4px}
  .rank-row .bar-track{grid-column:1 / -1;height:16px}
  .match{grid-template-columns:58px 1fr;row-gap:8px}
  .match .pred,.match .conf-wrap{grid-column:2}
  .live-row{grid-template-columns:1fr;row-gap:6px}
  .live-row .when{order:1}.live-row .teams{order:2}.live-row .pred-small{order:3}
  .live-row .score-in{order:4;justify-content:flex-start}.live-row .outcome{order:5;justify-self:start}
  .stat-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .pool-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .detail{padding:10px}
  .detail-card{padding:20px 16px;max-height:92vh}
  .detail-card h3{font-size:20px}
  .scatter-box{padding:14px 8px;overflow-x:auto}
  #scatter{min-width:560px}
  .standings,.disagree-table,.md-compare{display:block;overflow-x:auto;white-space:nowrap}
  .sort-bar,.slider-bar{font-size:11px}
  .slider-bar input[type=range]{width:150px}
  .slider-bar .count{width:100%;margin-left:0;order:5}
  .cards{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .calib{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  h1{font-size:clamp(26px,8vw,40px)}
}
@media(max-width:420px){
  .cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .rank-team{font-size:12.5px}
  .match .teams{font-size:12.5px}
}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.page.active{animation:none}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
<header>
  <div class="eyebrow">Predictive model · 48 teams · 4 weighted variables</div>
  <h1>World Cup <span>2026</span><br>Model Dashboard</h1>
  <p class="sub">A 48-team predictive model created by <b>Moby</b> for the 2026 FIFA World Cup fantasy season. Four weighted variables, validated against the 2022 tournament and the betting market. Data sources: eloratings.net (ELO), Flashscore/Opta (xG), Transfermarkt (squad values), Oddschecker (market odds), openfootball (live results). Final pre-tournament snapshot: <b>10 June 2026</b> — full calculation details under Methodology.</p>
</header>

<nav>
  <button class="active" data-page="rankings">Rankings</button>
  <button data-page="pools">Pools</button>
  <button data-page="market">Model vs Market</button>
  <button data-page="matches">All Matches</button>
  <button data-page="live">Live Results</button>
  <button data-page="poisson">Live Model</button>
  <button data-page="method">Methodology</button>
</nav>

<section id="rankings" class="page active">
  <h2>Composite strength ranking</h2>
  <p class="note">Each bar splits a team's composite score into its weighted components — not just how strong a team is, but why. Click a team for the full profile including squad details and the last 10 matches.</p>
  <div class="legend">
    <span><i class="dot" style="background:var(--elo)"></i>ELO (45%)</span>
    <span><i class="dot" style="background:var(--form)"></i>Form (25%)</span>
    <span><i class="dot" style="background:var(--xg)"></i>xG diff (20%)</span>
    <span><i class="dot" style="background:var(--squad)"></i>Squad value (10%)</span>
    <span><i class="dot" style="background:var(--gold)"></i>Host nation bonus (+0.073)</span>
    <span style="color:var(--warn)">×G = xG excluded (weights redistributed)</span>
  </div>
  <div id="rank-list"></div>
</section>

<section id="pools" class="page">
  <h2>Pool analysis</h2>
  <div class="pool-select" id="pool-select"></div>
  <div class="subtabs">
    <button class="active" data-sub="teams">Teams</button>
    <button data-sub="standings">Predicted standings</button>
  </div>
  <div id="sub-teams">
    <div class="pool-grid" id="pool-teams"></div>
    <div class="pool-matches"><h3>Group stage fixtures</h3><div id="pool-match-list"></div></div>
  </div>
  <div id="sub-standings" style="display:none">
    <table class="standings">
      <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Team</th><th>Pred. Pts</th><th>W</th><th>D</th><th>L</th><th>Composite</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody id="standings-body"></tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="qual-note"><span style="color:var(--xg)">■</span> Top 2 advance directly. <span style="color:var(--third)">■</span> Predicted 3rd-place finisher ranked among the 8 best thirds across all pools — these also advance to the round of 32. Standings derived from match predictions: win = 3 pts, too close to call = 1 pt each; composite score breaks ties.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="market" class="page">
  <h2>Model vs betting market</h2>
  <p class="note">Composite score against the market's implied tournament-winner probability. Hover any point to identify the team. The dashed line is a least-squares trend fitted in the plotted space — teams above it are rated higher by the model than the market consensus, teams below it lower.</p>
  <div class="scatter-box">
    <svg id="scatter" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 900 520"></svg>
    <div class="tooltip" id="tooltip"></div>
  </div>
  <h2 style="font-size:16px">Biggest disagreements</h2>
  <p class="note">Model rank vs market rank. Positive gap = your model rates them higher than the market.</p>
  <table class="disagree-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Team</th><th>Model rank</th><th>Market rank</th><th>Gap</th><th>Reading</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody id="disagree-body"></tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 style="font-size:16px;margin-top:34px">Hit-rate race · three predictors</h2>
  <p class="note">As results come in, how each predictor is doing on decided matches: your frozen pre-tournament model, the live-updating Poisson model, and the betting market (the pre-match favourite by implied tournament odds). Updates automatically from the openfootball feed.</p>
  <div class="cards" id="race-cards"></div>

  <h2 style="font-size:16px;margin-top:22px">Per-match: model probability vs market favourite</h2>
  <p class="note">For each fixture, the live Poisson win probability for the market's favourite team. Points well below 50% are matches where your model disagrees with the bookmakers' pick — the most interesting ones to watch.</p>
  <div class="scatter-box"><svg id="mm-scatter" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 900 460"></svg><div class="tooltip" id="mm-tip"></div></div>
</section>

<section id="matches" class="page">
  <h2>All group stage matches</h2>
